# startDate

**Instance Property**

The start date of the timed metadata.

## Declaration

```swift
var startDate: Date? { get }
```

## Discussion

The value is `nil` if the metadata item doesn’t provide a start date.

## Accessing timing

- **time**: The timestamp of the metadata item.
- **duration**: The duration of the metadata item.
